                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2512.05103/figs/ex_for_teaser/frame_1.jpg",
                "caption": "Figure 1:Overview of TV2TV interleaved text and video generation.TV2TV is a unified generative modeling framework which decomposes video generation into an interleaved text and video generation process. During inference, TV2TV dynamically alternates between autoregressively generating plans in text and semi-autoregressively generating chunks of video frames, allowing the model tothink in wordsabout the content of the subsequent frames beforeacting in pixelsto produce those frames. This framework enables fine-grained and flexible control during video generation, allowing users to potentially intervene and modify the video generation trajectory at any point through textual prompting.",
